      <title>马杜罗（Maduro</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/maduro-shuffles-central-bank-board-amid-push-to-boost-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉的两名中央银行董事在尼古拉斯·马杜罗（NicolásMaduro）总统对将大量黄金纳入国际储备中发表评论后，留下了职位，这引起了人们对使用不受监管的矿山来加强该国库存的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/maduro-shuffles-central-bank-board-amid-push-to-boost-reserves</guid>
